{
  "stem": "1062.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, we were marched out to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Marched out from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we were going, you know, the snow piled up because I had wooden-- leather shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the-- when you have a lump on your foot, and it's wood, so you start going like a duck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could clean it up sometimes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what happened, people didn't have enough strength.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after a while, they would just sit down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Once you sat down in the-- everybody passed through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the-- from behind, there was a-- there was German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would shoot you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Once you stayed behind, they kill you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in my transport, I personally didn't see it, but somebody told me and I remember this, that one German sat down, a German soldier, took his rifle, put it in his mouth and pulled the trigger.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He killed himself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah, he killed himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Apparently he was a good Nazi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I want you to know what happened to me up to this point, and I'm talking 1945, is nothing compared to what's going to happen now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That night-- the following day-- we marched all night, all night, all night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The following day we marched and one night we came to a place called Nikolaev.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a big, big farm over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was one, one, one house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One building, like a barn or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I went into the barn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And everybody tried to get into that barn, but there was no room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the barn, they had some beams across.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I climbed up and I sat on the beam.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
